Titolo: Pearl's Peril

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Pearl’s Peril is a hidden object game developed by Berlin-based Wooga. It was launched on 5 March 2013 on the Facebook social media platform and on 5 September on iPad. Pearl’s Peril is Wooga’s sixth game, and was the company’s fastest growing game at the time. Wooga also released a soundtrack to the game.

Genere: Hidden Object 

Valutazione: N/A
